en.title: Teyvat Chapter Interlude Teaser: The Gods' Limits | Genshin Impact #GenshinImpact
en.description:
In the council of gods, no mortal voice is ever heard.
And thus was the fate of the world arbitrarily determined.
We know that such is the way of the world.
But do the gods act out of contempt...
Or have they at some hour begun to act out of fear?

snippet.title: FLY vs. BLG â€” MSI 2025 â€” Bracket Stage
snippet.description:
MSI 2025, LIVE FROM VANCOUVER #msi2025 

The 2025 League of Legends Mid-Season Invitational is hereâ€”bringing together the five regions to battle for glory, pride, and a critical edge heading into Worlds. As the second international showdown on the LoL Esports calendar, MSI pits two representatives from each regional league against one another in a high-stakes clash that tests their mettle at the seasonâ€™s halfway mark. More than just a trophy is on the line: the winning team and the next best-performing region will earn extra slots at the World Championship, raising the stakes even higher. This year, the action unfolds beginning June 27 at the iconic Pacific Coliseum in Vancouver, Canada. Get ready for rivalries, redemption arcs, and unforgettable plays as pros will be challenged to Ignite The Fire Within.

PLAY-INS STAGE: June 27-June 29
BRACKET STAGE: July 1-July 12

You can always learn more and view the full match schedule at http://www.lolesports.com.

snippet.title: The Truth About Kevin Durant's Nets Experience | LeBron James & Steve Nash | MIND THE GAME
snippet.description:
Kevin Durant is back for part 2 and heâ€™s still dropping gems. In this conversation he tells LeBron James and Steve Nash why he fell in love with the game, how he earned respect on the court at a young age, and all about the achilles injury recovery process including his advice to Jayson Tatum, Damian Lillard, and Tyrese Haliburton.

Durant and Nash, his former coach on the Brooklyn Nets, share what exactly happened during their time together and why they werenâ€™t able to fully reach their potential. Nash also gives sage advice to his counterparts on how to transition from your playing days to the next stage of life. 

Catch up with Part 1 of KD's guest appearance: https://youtu.be/VUzP2PvXeoY

Presented by UNINTERRUPTED and Wondery.

(0:00) - Intro
(1:11) - Why Ime Udoka (Houston Rockets) and Erik Spoelstra (Miami Heat) are special coaches
(12:30) - How KD fell in love with the game
(16:35) - KD on his mother believing in him
(19:20) - Why players have to be obsessed to be great
(25:53) - KD on every contract being a re-commitment to yourself
(30:45) - Steveâ€™s perspective on retirement
(33:52) - KDâ€™s achilles injury advice to Jayson Tatum and Damian Lillard
(38:07) - KD and Steve share what really happened in Brooklyn
(40:03) - Why Steve was unable to reach his full potential as Nets coach

New episodes drop every Tuesday. Watch Mind The Game with LeBron James and Steve Nash for NBA interviews, analysis, highlights and more. Subscribe to our YouTube Channel, watch on Prime Video or follow Mind The Game wherever you listen to podcasts.

thank you to: egg, @sharpnessyt, @4CVIT, @loppezz

snippet.title: I Quit.
snippet.description:
Hey, everyone. It's me, Quackity. I just want to share with everyone that I am approaching a new phase in my life. This video has been in the works for a long time, and I hope everyone can watch in it's entirety. Nearly three years ago I inadvertently quit my main platform where I was making content, and ever since then, Iâ€™ve been working on a lot of projects which I am incredibly proud of.

Today, I want to announce my biggest project yet.

Dababel.

This is a project which I hold very dear to my heart, not because of what it is, but because of what it represents to me. I was born and raised in Mexico, my native language is Spanish - and this gave me the opportunity to experience what it was like to be in another country and not know the language. Throughout my life and my career Iâ€™ve noticed how prevalent language barriers are - no matter where you are. And Dababel is a project with the objective to help people move beyond this barrier, which has existed since the beginning of time.

This is a project for you. This is a project for everyone.

DABABEL IS FOR THE WORLD. 

Thank you for all the support, and I hope you enjoy Dababel. To my global communities, to my new viewers and old, thank you for everything!

snippet.title: Timelapse shows Texas flash floods turn dry river into deadly rapids in 20 minutes
snippet.description:
Dramatic timelapse video shows how heavy rainfall turned a dry riverbed into surging rapids in just 20 minutes, as Texas was deluged by deadly flash floods on July 4.

CCTV footage shows water begin surging into the Llano River at 17:14. Within minutes, a road crossing the river is entirely submerged, with the waterline rising significantly on both sides of the riverbank and completely covering trees and bushes.

snippet.title: Jay Leno's ULTIMATE GM Restomods: Buick, Chevy, & Oldsmobile! | Jay Leno's Garage
snippet.description:
Join Jay Leno in a special episode of Jay Leno's Garage as he showcases three incredible General Motors restomods that were built for SEMA, including a Hot Rod of the Year winner! With the invaluable help of GM engineers like Tony Roma, these classic American cars have been transformed into modern powerhouses while retaining their iconic styling.

1. The 1955 Buick Roadmaster: Jay recounts the personal history of his '55 Buick, from buying it out of the PennySaver to getting married in it. See how it was transformed with a 572 crate engine, C5 Corvette suspension, and disc brakes, making this vintage Buick able to "blow off a Corvette!" 

2. The 1932 Bowtie Deuce Roadster:

 Celebrating the 50th anniversary of the small-block V8, this '32 Chevy body sits on a '34 Chevy chassis and is powered by a 427 LS7 engine with 600 horsepower and a 6-speed manual gearbox. Discover the unique diamond-infused paint  and the challenges of building a classic hot rod with modern performance.

3. The 1966 Oldsmobile Toronado:

The Hot Rod of the Year winner in 2006, this Toronado is a true marvel. Originally a groundbreaking front-wheel-drive car , Jay's restomod features a custom chassis, a 427 LS7 engine with twin turbochargers , and over 1000 horsepower! Learn about its unique engineering, including custom-made wheels and a solid 50/50 weight distribution.

Experience these "bulletproof" builds, the challenges of working with extreme power, and the joy of driving these American legends!

en.title: Jay Leno's ULTIMATE GM Restomods: Buick, Chevy, & Oldsmobile! | Jay Leno's Garage
en.description:
Join Jay Leno in a special episode of Jay Leno's Garage as he showcases three incredible General Motors restomods that were built for SEMA, including a Hot Rod of the Year winner! With the invaluable help of GM engineers like Tony Roma, these classic American cars have been transformed into modern powerhouses while retaining their iconic styling.

1. The 1955 Buick Roadmaster: Jay recounts the personal history of his '55 Buick, from buying it out of the PennySaver to getting married in it. See how it was transformed with a 572 crate engine, C5 Corvette suspension, and disc brakes, making this vintage Buick able to "blow off a Corvette!" 

2. The 1932 Bowtie Deuce Roadster:

 Celebrating the 50th anniversary of the small-block V8, this '32 Chevy body sits on a '34 Chevy chassis and is powered by a 427 LS7 engine with 600 horsepower and a 6-speed manual gearbox. Discover the unique diamond-infused paint  and the challenges of building a classic hot rod with modern performance.

3. The 1966 Oldsmobile Toronado:

The Hot Rod of the Year winner in 2006, this Toronado is a true marvel. Originally a groundbreaking front-wheel-drive car , Jay's restomod features a custom chassis, a 427 LS7 engine with twin turbochargers , and over 1000 horsepower! Learn about its unique engineering, including custom-made wheels and a solid 50/50 weight distribution.

Experience these "bulletproof" builds, the challenges of working with extreme power, and the joy of driving these American legends!

id.title: GM Restomod TERBAIK Jay Leno: Buick, Chevy, & Oldsmobile! | Garasi Jay Leno
id.description:
Bergabunglah dengan Jay Leno dalam episode spesial Jay Leno's Garage saat ia memamerkan tiga mobil General Motors yang luar biasa yang dibuat untuk SEMA, termasuk pemenang Hot Rod of the Year! Dengan bantuan tak ternilai dari para insinyur GM seperti Tony Roma, mobil-mobil klasik Amerika ini telah diubah menjadi mobil-mobil modern yang bertenaga sambil mempertahankan gaya ikoniknya.

1. Buick Roadmaster 1955: Jay menceritakan sejarah pribadi Buick '55 miliknya, dari membelinya dari PennySaver hingga menikah di dalamnya. Lihat bagaimana mobil itu diubah dengan mesin 572 crate, suspensi C5 Corvette, dan rem cakram, yang membuat Buick klasik ini mampu "melampaui Corvette!" 

2. Bowtie Deuce Roadster 1932:

Merayakan ulang tahun ke-50 mesin V8 blok kecil, bodi Chevy '32 ini berada di atas sasis Chevy '34 dan ditenagai oleh mesin 427 LS7 dengan tenaga 600 tenaga kuda dan transmisi manual 6 percepatan. Temukan cat unik yang diresapi berlian dan tantangan dalam membangun mobil hot rod klasik dengan performa modern.

3. Oldsmobile Toronado 1966:

Pemenang Hot Rod of the Year pada tahun 2006, Toronado ini benar-benar luar biasa. Awalnya merupakan mobil penggerak roda depan yang inovatif, restomod Jay menampilkan sasis khusus, mesin 427 LS7 dengan turbocharger ganda, dan lebih dari 1000 tenaga kuda! Pelajari tentang rekayasa uniknya, termasuk roda yang dibuat khusus dan distribusi berat 50/50 yang solid.

Rasakan pengalaman membangun kendaraan "antipeluru" ini, tantangan bekerja dengan tenaga ekstrem, dan kegembiraan mengendarai legenda Amerika ini!

it.description:

Con il prezioso aiuto di ingegneri GM come Tony Roma, queste classiche auto americane sono state trasformate in moderni propulsori, pur mantenendo il loro stile iconico.

1. La Buick Roadmaster del 1955: Jay racconta la storia personale della sua Buick del '55, dall'acquisto da PennySaver al matrimonio a bordo. Scopri come Ã¨ stata trasformata con un motore 572 a cassa, sospensioni da Corvette C5 e freni a disco, rendendo questa Buick d'epoca in grado di "spazzare via una Corvette!".

2. Bowtie Deuce Roadster del 1932:

Per celebrare il 50Â° anniversario del motore V8 small-block, questa Chevy del '32 Ã¨ costruita su un telaio Chevy del '34 ed Ã¨ alimentata da un motore 427 LS7 da 600 cavalli e cambio manuale a 6 marce. Scopri l'esclusiva vernice diamantata e le sfide che comporta costruire una hot rod classica con prestazioni moderne.

3. Oldsmobile Toronado del 1966:

Vincitrice del premio Hot Rod dell'Anno nel 2006, questa Toronado Ã¨ una vera meraviglia. Originariamente un'auto rivoluzionaria a trazione anteriore, la restomod di Jay presenta un telaio personalizzato, un motore 427 LS7 con doppio turbocompressore e oltre 1000 cavalli di potenza! nl-NL.title: Jay Leno's ULTIEME GM Restomods: Buick, Chevy en Oldsmobile! | Jay Leno's Garage
nl-NL.description:
Sluit je aan bij Jay Leno in een speciale aflevering van Jay Leno's Garage, waarin hij drie ongelooflijke General Motors restomods laat zien die speciaal voor SEMA zijn gebouwd, waaronder een Hot Rod of the Year-winnaar! Met de onschatbare hulp van GM-ingenieurs zoals Tony Roma zijn deze klassieke Amerikaanse auto's omgetoverd tot moderne krachtpatsers, met behoud van hun iconische stijl.

1. De Buick Roadmaster uit 1955: Jay vertelt over de persoonlijke geschiedenis van zijn Buick uit '55, van de aankoop uit de PennySaver tot zijn huwelijk erin. Zie hoe hij werd omgebouwd met een 572 kratmotor, C5 Corvette-vering en schijfremmen, waardoor deze vintage Buick "een Corvette kan overtreffen!" 2. De Bowtie Deuce Roadster uit 1932:

Deze '32 Chevy-carrosserie, die het 50-jarig jubileum van de small-block V8 viert, staat op een '34 Chevy-chassis en wordt aangedreven door een 427 LS7-motor met 600 pk en een handgeschakelde zesversnellingsbak. Ontdek de unieke diamantgeÃ¯nfuseerde lak en de uitdagingen van het bouwen van een klassieke hot rod met moderne prestaties.

3. De Oldsmobile Toronado uit 1966:

Deze Toronado, winnaar van de Hot Rod of the Year-prijs in 2006, is een waar wonder. Oorspronkelijk een baanbrekende auto met voorwielaandrijving, beschikt Jay's restomod over een aangepast chassis, een 427 LS7-motor met dubbele turbo en meer dan 1000 pk! Ontdek de unieke techniek, inclusief op maat gemaakte velgen en een solide 50/50-gewichtsverdeling.

Ervaar deze "kogelvrije" bouwwerken, de uitdagingen van het werken met extreme kracht en het plezier van het besturen van deze Amerikaanse legendes!

Koop autoverzorgings- en detailproducten bij Jay Leno's Garage: https://www.lenosgarage.com/shine

snippet.title: THIS PIZZA CHALLENGE IN FLORIDA HAS ONLY BEEN BEATEN ONCE! | BeardMeatsFood
snippet.description:
In this week's episode we're at Crostini's Pizza & Cuisine in Deltona, Florida having a crack at their 28" pizza challenge...

Teams of two get just 28 minutes in which to finish a 28" pizza (with toppings of their choice...or just plain cheese if you're feeling a bit soggy) and if successful, not only is the meal ON THE HOUSE but you get a $50 gift card for your troubles too! It's been a while since I tried a team pizza challenge, so I gave my old mate @WayneAlgenio a call to help me try to secure the win!

FOLLOW ME: @BeardMeatsFood

WATCH THE PODCAST: https://www.youtube.com/@BreakingBeardPod

FOLLOW THE PODCAST: @BreakingBeardPod

snippet.title: I Tried an Ultra Luxury Ritz Carlton Cruise
snippet.description:
Get started with Odoo today: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR 
Iâ€™m getting onboard one of the worldâ€™s most luxurious cruise ships, the brand new Ritz Carlton Yacht, Ilma. Iâ€™ve booked a signature suite for the next 7 days, and Iâ€™ll be showing you everything this First Class ship has to offer. From the many restaurants (including a 10 course tasting menu for $700!), the pools, floating marina and we shall even take a look at the best room onboard, the owners suite. 

For reference as usual I paid in full for this cruise, as I donâ€™t work with the cruise lines, to the tune of over $28,000 dollars! Itâ€™s actually not my first time onboard a Ritz Carlton Yacht, having tried their previous ship Evrima a couple of years ago. There were quite a few teething issues onboard that sailing, so Iâ€™m keen to see how theyâ€™ve changed (or if they have!) with the addition of Ilma and Luminara. These new ships are larger, with even more staterooms and facilities. As always do let me know what you think down below.

id.description:

Saya telah memesan suite khusus untuk 7 hari ke depan, dan saya akan menunjukkan kepada Anda semua yang ditawarkan kapal Kelas Utama ini. Dari banyak restoran (termasuk menu mencicipi 10 hidangan seharga $700!), kolam renang, marina terapung, dan kita bahkan akan melihat kamar terbaik di atas kapal, suite pemilik. 

Sebagai referensi seperti biasa, saya membayar penuh untuk pelayaran ini, karena saya tidak bekerja dengan perusahaan pelayaran, dengan jumlah lebih dari $28.000 dolar! Sebenarnya ini bukan pertama kalinya saya naik Ritz Carlton Yacht, setelah mencoba kapal mereka sebelumnya Evrima beberapa tahun yang lalu. Ada beberapa masalah awal di atas pelayaran itu, jadi saya ingin melihat bagaimana mereka telah berubah (atau apakah mereka telah berubah!) dengan penambahan Ilma dan Luminara. Kapal-kapal baru ini lebih besar, dengan lebih banyak kabin dan fasilitas. Seperti biasa, beri tahu saya pendapat Anda di bawah ini.

nl-NL.title: Ik heb een ultra-luxe Ritz Carlton-cruise geprobeerd
nl-NL.description:
Begin vandaag nog met Odoo: https://www.odoo.com/r/ksR
Ik ga aan boord van een van 's werelds meest luxueuze cruiseschepen, de gloednieuwe Ritz Carlton Yacht, de Ilma. Ik heb een signature suite geboekt voor de komende 7 dagen en ik laat je alles zien wat dit eersteklas schip te bieden heeft. Van de vele restaurants (inclusief een 10-gangen proeverijmenu voor $ 700!), de zwembaden, de drijvende jachthaven, tot de beste kamer aan boord: de eigenaarssuite.

Ter referentie: zoals gewoonlijk heb ik deze cruise volledig betaald, omdat ik niet met rederijen werk, voor meer dan $ 28.000! Het is niet de eerste keer dat ik aan boord ga van een Ritz Carlton Yacht. Ik heb een paar jaar geleden hun vorige schip, de Evrima, geprobeerd. Er waren nogal wat kinderziektes aan boord van die cruise, dus ik ben benieuwd hoe ze zijn veranderd (of dat ze dat al zijn!) met de toevoeging van Ilma en Luminara. Deze nieuwe schepen zijn groter, met nog meer hutten en faciliteiten. Laat me zoals altijd hieronder weten wat je ervan vindt.

snippet.title: Floods devastate Texas hill country as death toll approaches 70
snippet.description:
President Donald Trump has approved federal disaster assistance for the state of Texas to assist in recovery efforts after massive floods destroyed dozens of homes and killed nearly 70 people. The funding is available to affected individuals in Kerr County, with assistance including grants for temporary housing and home repairs, low-cost loans to cover uninsured property, and various other recovery programs. Funding will also be available to state and local governments, as well as certain nonprofits, for emergency work and the repair of critical infrastructure, as well as the repair or replacement of facilities.

localized.title: Floods devastate Texas hill country as death toll approaches 70
localized.description:
President Donald Trump has approved federal disaster assistance for the state of Texas to assist in recovery efforts after massive floods destroyed dozens of homes and killed nearly 70 people. The funding is available to affected individuals in Kerr County, with assistance including grants for temporary housing and home repairs, low-cost loans to cover uninsured property, and various other recovery programs. Funding will also be available to state and local governments, as well as certain nonprofits, for emergency work and the repair of critical infrastructure, as well as the repair or replacement of facilities.

snippet.title: Alex Bowman on Bubba Wallace: "I Really Thought We Had Squashed Our Beef, but Clearly We Haven't"
snippet.description:
Alex Bowman voices his thoughts on the late race contact with Bubba Wallace following the NASCAR Cup Series race at Chicago. Bowman and Wallace raced hard as the laps winded down which ended with Wallace spinning off the No. 48 team's bumper. Frontstretch's Bryan Nolen was among those who spoke to Bowman after the race.

snippet.title: How do Minecraft computers work?
snippet.description:
Today I learn to build Minecraft redstone computers, with expert lesson from Computational Redstone YouTuber  @mattbatwings   . Mattbatwings has built pacman in Minecraft, Super Mario Bros in Minecraft, Flappy bird in Minecraft and so much more - a lot of these giant redstone contraptions are featured in this video. Matt also does a tutorial on Computational redstone, covering the fundaments of Minecraft redstone logic, and even gets me to build my first computational redstone contraption.

MATTS CHANNEL: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
GO WATCH EVERYTHING HE HAS MADE!!

Matt geeft ook een tutorial over Computational Redstone, waarin hij de basis van Minecraft redstone logica behandelt, en hij laat me zelfs mijn eerste computational Redstone-apparaat bouwen.

MATTS KANAAL: https://www.youtube.com/@mattbatwings
GA KIJKEN NAAR ALLES WAT HIJ HEEFT GEMAAKT!!

snippet.title: Search and recovery efforts continue across the flood ravaged Hill Country
snippet.description:
Flash floods in Texas killed at least 82 people over the Fourth of July holiday weekend and left others still missing, including girls attending a summer camp. The devastation along the Guadalupe River, outside of San Antonio, has drawn a massive search effort as officials face questions over their preparedness and the speed of their initial actions.

snippet.title: Death toll in central Texas flash floods rises to 79 as sheriff says 10 campers remain missing
snippet.description:
Families sifted through waterlogged debris Sunday and stepped inside empty cabins at Camp Mystic, an all-girls summer camp ripped apart by flash floods that washed homes off their foundations and killed at least 79 people in central Texas.

Rescuers maneuvering through challenging terrain continued their desperate search for the missing, including 10 girls and a counselor from the camp. For the first time since the storms began pounding Texas, Gov. Greg Abbott said there were 41 people confirmed to be unaccounted for across the state and more could be missing.

Read more at: https://www.9news.com/article/news/nation-world/texas-floods-campers-missing/507-2c41ffb5-638c-4d53-bc6b-a444a0618bdb

id.title: Deep Raih ENAM Poin Saat India Menang di Edgbaston! | Cuplikan - Inggris v India Hari ke-5 | Tes ...
id.description:
Kunjungi ecb.co.uk untuk bergabung dengan We Are England Cricket Supporters secara gratis dan dapatkan akses prioritas ke tiket dan banyak lagi!

Saksikan cuplikan pertandingan dari Hari ke-5 Tes Rothesay antara Inggris dan India di Edgbaston, Birmingham

Ini adalah saluran resmi ECB. Saksikan semua video terbaru dari tim Kriket Inggris dan Dewan Kriket Inggris dan Wales, termasuk cuplikan, wawancara, dan fitur yang akan membuat Anda lebih dekat dengan tim Inggris dan pemain daerah.

Berlangganan untuk informasi selengkapnya: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ecbcricket

Menampilkan video dari tim kriket Inggris, Vitality Blast, Kejuaraan Daerah, Piala Satu Hari Metro Bank, dan banyak lagi.

snippet.title: Texas flooding timelapse: Guadalupe River jumps 19 feet an an hour
snippet.description:
In less than an hour, the Guadalupe River in Texas went from 1 1/2 feet to 20 feet. As of Monday morning, 82 are confirmed to have died with another ten still missing.

FOX 2 Detroit is working for you and delivers breaking news, live events, investigations, politics, entertainment, business news and local stories from Detroit, Michigan, and across the nation.

snippet.title: The evidence that damned Piastri in Verstappen British GP controversy
snippet.description:
A penalty for erratic driving decided the British Grand Prix as an aggrieved Oscar Piastri lost victory to McLaren team-mate and F1 title rival Lando Norris. 

This wet and wild Silverstone F1 race came down to one key moment: the restart on lap 21, when Piastriâ€™s braking caught Verstappen out. Jon Noble and Scott Mitchell-Malm delve into the data that doomed Piastri.

01:43 Piastri's double trouble
03:10 Verstappen's view

05:40 McLaren suggests gamesmanship
07:48 Piastri's cheeky swap request

This wet and wild Silverstone F1 race came down to one key moment: the restart on lap 21, when Piastriâ€™s braking caught Verstappen out. Jon Noble and Scott Mitchell-Malm delve into the data that doomed Piastri.

00:00 How Piastri lost victory
01:43 Piastri's double trouble
03:10 Verstappen's view
04:17 Why Canada was different
05:40 McLaren suggests gamesmanship
07:48 Piastri's cheeky swap request
08:46 Title race implications 

READ MORE HERE: https://www.the-race.com/formula-1/why-oscar-piastri-got-race-costing-british-gp-f1-penalty-erratic-braking/

Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything â€” be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer â€œCapture the Flagâ€ game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (â€œRobuxâ€). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

id.description:
**Dalam Kenangan Penuh Kasih untuk Coach Tyler Wall**

Dengan kesedihan yang mendalam, kami menyampaikan kabar meninggalnya Pelatih Tyler Wall. Pelatih Wall adalah sosok luar biasa yang kebaikan dan semangatnya yang tulus menyentuh hati semua orang yang mengenalnya. Kehilangannya membuat hati kami sangat berduka.

Menyusul berita tragis ini, kami menghubungi keluarga Pelatih Wall untuk menentukan apakah video ini harus dibagikan. Dengan keanggunan dan kebijaksanaan, mereka menyatakan bahwa Tyler ingin pesannya yang penuh harapan dan kepositifan terus menjangkau orang lain, bahkan saat ia tidak ada.

Kami dengan rendah hati meminta Anda untuk menghormati kenangan Pelatih Wall dan menghargai kebutuhan keluarganya akan privasi selama masa sulit ini.

Warisan kasih sayang dan dorongan Pelatih Tyler Wall akan terus hidup di hati semua orang yang cukup beruntung untuk mengenalnya.

Mulailah bisnis yang kamu impikan dan kunjungi https://www.Shopify.com/MrBeast untuk memulai uji coba kamu sekarang.

snippet.title: Belton, Texas teen rescued from deadly Guadalupe River floods
snippet.description:
BELTON, Texas (KWTX) - Belton teenager Riata Schoepf was rescue by first responders on Friday after being swept away by the deadly Guadalupe River floods.

Riata went on vacation to Hunt, Texas with another family for the Fourth of July. Their hotel bordered the Guadalupe River. Her dad, Ronnie Schoepf, recalled his daughters experience being evacuated.

â€œShe says around 2:30 or so sheâ€™s hearing loud thunder and lightning and then the next thing she knew somebodyâ€™s banging on her door telling everybody they need to get out,â€ Ronnie said.

Riata and her group took to their vehicles to escape the flooding, but traffic was at a standstill. Water then began to rise around their car.

snippet.title: Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
David is dead. But Night City lives on.
Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is now in production!

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 presents a new standalone 10-episode story from the world of Cyberpunk 2077â€” a raw chronicle of redemption and revenge. In a city that thrives in the spotlight of violence, one question remains: when the world is blinded by spectacle, what extremes do you have to go to make your story matter?

Director Kai Ikarashi (Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, SSSS.Gridman) brings a bold, cinematic vision to the series, supported by the lead character designer Kanno Ichigo (Promare, Cyberpunk: Edgerunners). They're joined by returning collaborators Masahiko Otsuka (Gurren Lagann, Promare) and Hugo Award winner Bartosz Sztybor as Showrunner, Story Writer, and Producer.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is created in collaboration with CD PROJEKT RED and animation studio TRIGGER, with a planned release on Netflix in the future.

snippet.title: Texas flooding survivor & witness reaction to Kerrville damage, search & rescues: 'Complete shock'
snippet.description:
A Kerrville resident said he and his wife were taken 200 feet down the Guadalupe River and managed to survive while his home was damaged by the flooding.

"It was scary," Scott Walden said while describing the speed of which the water rose. "It was really scary."

Meanwhile, a Pennsylvania woman visiting family in the area said she remains in shock, especially given the volume of missing adults and children, many from Camp Mystic.

"It's not going to be a good ending," Tonia Fucci said. "There's no way people could have survived the swiftness of the water."

snippet.title: Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 | Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
David is dead. But Night City lives on.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is now in production!

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 presents a new standalone 10-episode story from the world of Cyberpunk 2077â€” a raw chronicle of redemption and revenge. In a city that thrives in the spotlight of violence, one question remains: when the world is blinded by spectacle, what extremes do you have to go to make your story matter?

Director Kai Ikarashi (Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, SSSS.Gridman) brings a bold, cinematic vision to the series, supported by the lead character designer Kanno Ichigo (Promare, Cyberpunk: Edgerunners). They're joined by returning collaborators Masahiko Otsuka (Gurren Lagann, Promare) and Hugo Award winner Bartosz Sztybor as Showrunner, Story Writer, and Producer.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is created in collaboration with CD PROJEKT RED and animation studio TRIGGER, with a planned release on Netflix in the future.

Music: â€œDiveâ€ by Beach House. Licensed courtesy of Sub Pop Records.

Stay connected, choom:

en.title: Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 | Announcement Teaser
en.description:
David is dead. But Night City lives on.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is now in production!

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 presents a new standalone 10-episode story from the world of Cyberpunk 2077â€” a raw chronicle of redemption and revenge. In a city that thrives in the spotlight of violence, one question remains: when the world is blinded by spectacle, what extremes do you have to go to make your story matter?

Director Kai Ikarashi (Cyberpunk: Edgerunners, SSSS.Gridman) brings a bold, cinematic vision to the series, supported by the lead character designer Kanno Ichigo (Promare, Cyberpunk: Edgerunners). They're joined by returning collaborators Masahiko Otsuka (Gurren Lagann, Promare) and Hugo Award winner Bartosz Sztybor as Showrunner, Story Writer, and Producer.

Cyberpunk: Edgerunners 2 is created in collaboration with CD PROJEKT RED and animation studio TRIGGER, with a planned release on Netflix in the future.

Music: â€œDiveâ€ by Beach House. Licensed courtesy of Sub Pop Records.

Stay connected, choom:

https://www.instagram.com/edgerunners/

snippet.title: Heartbreaking Search After Texas Floods: Man Separated From Wife in Torrential Waters
snippet.description: Flooding has devastated parts of Texas, with dozens of water rescues reported across Kerr County. One man, swept away while camping with his wife, shared his emotional story as he continues to search for her. Emergency crews have been working around the clock with state and federal resources deployed to assist with rescues and reunifications. A local school has become a reunification hub as families wait for news on missing loved ones. The damage across the area reveals just how powerful the floodwaters were.

ENTER THE ARENA
Build your Battle Deck and outsmart the enemy in fast real-time battles. From the creators of CLASH OF CLANS comes a real-time multiplayer battle game starring your favourite Clash characters and more. Start battling against players from around the world!

BECOME A MASTER OF STRATEGY AND DECK BUILDING
Choose unique Cards to your Battle Deck and head to the Arena for Battle!
Place your Cards right and knock down the enemy King and Princesses from their Towers in a strategic and fast-paced match.

COLLECT AND UPGRADE 100+ CARDS
Hog Rider! Collect and upgrade 100+ Cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defences you know and love and many others. Win battles and progress to new Arenas to unlock powerful new Cards to your collection!

BATTLE YOUR WAY TO THE TOP
Battle your way to the League and Global Tournaments to match against the best players in the world.
Compete for glory and rewards!

SEASONAL EVENTS
Unlock new Seasonal items like Tower Skins, Emotes and powerful Magic Items with the Season Pass and participate in fun Challenges that put your skills to the test!

JOIN A CLAN AND GO TO WAR
Join or form a Clan with other players to share Cards and battle in Clan Wars for BIG rewards!

See you in the Arena!
#ClashRoyale

snippet.title: Jason Momoa Causes CHAOS in the Pit at Ozzy Osbourne's Final Show
snippet.description:
We knew this show would be legendary, and Birmingham did not disappoint! This massive event was a monumental celebration of Ozzy Osborne and Black Sabbath, featuring a "who's who" of rock royalty. We witnessed incredible performances from Lizzy Hale, Papa V's epic "Bark at the Moon," Alice in Chains, and Lamb of God. The Slayer reunion, honoring Black Sabbath and Ozzy, was absolutely showstopping.

But the moment that truly broke the internet? Host Jason Momoa, during Pantera's absolutely crushing set, couldn't resist the call of the pit! He jumped in, completely lost in the moment, joining the mosh pit for Pantera's entire performance of "Hostel." Eyewitnesses saw him hugging fans and taking selfies â€“ a true testament to his love for the music. This historic party in Birmingham is still rocking, and Jason Momoa's sincerity and passion are undeniable!

--------------------------------------------------------------------
Hari ini, saya menemukan anggota berikutnya dari trinitas suci hypercar - Porsche 918 Spyder 2015. Dan seperti yang dapat Anda bayangkan, mobil itu adalah yang terburuk di planet ini. Mobil itu tidak hanya rusak karena kebakaran, tetapi juga telah terbengkalai selama lebih dari satu dekade. Dan kendala lainnya - mobil itu tidak ada di negara ini, jadi langkah pertama adalah mencoba membawanya masuk. Saya akan sangat beruntung.

nl-NL.title: Ik kocht een door brand beschadigde Porsche 918 Spyder van $ 2.000.000 en het is erger dan je je ...
nl-NL.description:
Bekijk de nieuwe Prijstrends-zoekfunctie van AutoTempest! â–º
https://www.autotempest.com/s/pVj8en
Of vind je volgende auto op AutoTempest! â–ºhttps://www.autotempest.com/s/Nm9hKm
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Vandaag heb ik het volgende lid van de hypercar-heilige drie-eenheid ontdekt: een Porsche 918 Spyder uit 2015. En zoals je je kunt voorstellen, is het de ergste ter wereld. Hij is niet alleen beschadigd door brand, maar staat ook al meer dan tien jaar verlaten. En nog een addertje onder het gras: hij staat niet in het land, dus de eerste stap is om hem binnen te halen. Ik heb al het geluk van de wereld nodig.

â—¼ï¸INTRODUCTION
Extravagant bloody battle involving love and desire, humans and devils, is coming to the big screens! 

â€œChainsaw Manâ€ is a manga serialized in Shueishaâ€™s â€œShonen Jump+â€ that has sold over 30,000,000 copies. In 2022, the series was broadcast as a TV Anime series that was made by animation studio MAPPA (Notable works: â€œJUJUTSU KAISENâ€, â€œAttack on Titan Final Seasonâ€, etc.), creating buzz all over the world.
Now in 2025, the episode that made the world go wild during its serialization is coming to theaters as an animated movie!

â—¼ï¸STORY
Denji (Kikunosuke Toya) became â€œChainsaw Manâ€, a boy with a devilâ€™s heart, and is now part of Special Division 4â€™s devil hunters. After a date with Makima (Tomori Kusunoki), the woman of his dreams, Denji takes shelter from the rain and meets a girl called Reze (Reina Ueda).
The girl, who works at a nearby cafÃ©, gives him a gentle smile, and they quickly grow close.
From this encounter onward, Denji's everyday life begins to change.

Extravagant bloody battle involving love and desire, humans and devils, is coming to the big screens! 

â€œChainsaw Manâ€ is a manga serialized in Shueishaâ€™s â€œShonen Jump+â€ that has sold over 30,000,000 copies. In 2022, the series was broadcast as a TV Anime series that was made by animation studio MAPPA (Notable works: â€œJUJUTSU KAISENâ€, â€œAttack on Titan Final Seasonâ€, etc.), creating buzz all over the world.
Now in 2025, the episode that made the world go wild during its serialization is coming to theaters as an animated movie!

â—¼ï¸STORY
Denji (Kikunosuke Toya) became â€œChainsaw Manâ€, a boy with a devilâ€™s heart, and is now part of Special Division 4â€™s devil hunters. After a date with Makima (Tomori Kusunoki), the woman of his dreams, Denji takes shelter from the rain and meets a girl called Reze (Reina Ueda).
The girl, who works at a nearby cafÃ©, gives him a gentle smile, and they quickly grow close.
From this encounter onward, Denji's everyday life begins to change.

snippet.title: MKOI vs. BLG | CFO vs. T1 â€” MSI 2025 â€” Bracket Stage
snippet.description:
MSI 2025, LIVE FROM VANCOUVER #msi2025 

The 2025 League of Legends Mid-Season Invitational is hereâ€”bringing together the five regions to battle for glory, pride, and a critical edge heading into Worlds. As the second international showdown on the LoL Esports calendar, MSI pits two representatives from each regional league against one another in a high-stakes clash that tests their mettle at the seasonâ€™s halfway mark. More than just a trophy is on the line: the winning team and the next best-performing region will earn extra slots at the World Championship, raising the stakes even higher. This year, the action unfolds beginning June 27 at the iconic Pacific Coliseum in Vancouver, Canada. Get ready for rivalries, redemption arcs, and unforgettable plays as pros will be challenged to Ignite The Fire Within.

PLAY-INS STAGE: June 27-June 29
BRACKET STAGE: July 1-July 12

You can always learn more and view the full match schedule at http://www.lolesports.com.

The 2025 League of Legends Mid-Season Invitational is hereâ€”bringing together the five regions to battle for glory, pride, and a critical edge heading into Worlds. As the second international showdown on the LoL Esports calendar, MSI pits two representatives from each regional league against one another in a high-stakes clash that tests their mettle at the seasonâ€™s halfway mark.
